'''Heloise Ruth First''' (4 May 1925 &#x2013; 17 Phuphu1982) Mongwadi wa Ditaba seakatemiki  le polotiki ramafolofolo. Obolailwe ko [[Mozambique]], moo  aberekile gona Kanako atsabile Afrika Borwa, ka parcel bomb e agilweng ka mapodisa a-Afrika Borwa.

== Lelapa le Thuto ==
E be ele ngwana wa mosetsana wa Jewish immigrants Julius le Matilda (new levetan) wa Pele . Julius mmopi wa di fenetshara ,o belegwe Latvia atla South Africa Ka 1906 a nale mengwaga ye lesome .Matilda o tlile South Africa anale mengwaga ye nne .E be ele maloko a mokgatlo wa leloko la mokgatlo wa  South Africa (CPSA, morago  South African Communist party[ SAPC] Ka 1921 . Ruth le butiagwe Ronald BA gotse bjalo Ka Di beiwa TSA Ka lapeng  moo batho kamoka ba go fapana ba boledisanang Gona Ka   tsa dipolotiki le moo batho  ba bangwe   ba ithutang gona.

O ile go fetsa marema tlou sekolong sa jeppe sa godimo sa basetsana , o ile Aya go ithutela yunibesithi ya  Witwatersrand, Johannesburg Ka 1942 go fihla Ka 1946 .O Ile a   a tswelela pele  ka BA (social studies),mola a hwetsa sociology, anthropology, economic history, anthropology history ya ekonomi le
